1) Download WoeUSB from here. (https://github.com/WoeUSB)
2) Plug in the pendrive. Delete the partion of the pendrive using "Disks" application in ubuntu. That's it for this step.
3) Run : sudo woeusb --target-filesystem NTFS --device 'location of windows ISO' 'target device' 
   -- Eg : sudo woeusb --target-filesystem NTFS --device '/home/sauravbilung/Downloads/Win10_20H2_v2_English_x64.iso' '/dev/sdb'
4) The process will take about 45 mins â€“ 50 mins to get completed.